name: Warfighter - .50 Cal Garrison Oscuro Maduro - Minutemen
additionalNotes: The Warfighter .50 Cal Garrison Oscuro Maduro is a medium strength cigar that is hand rolled by Plasencia Cigars in Nicaragua. It features a Honduran Habano maduro wrapper that covers a Honduran Connecticut binder, and a Habano filler. The Warfighter .50 Cal Garrison Oscuro Maduro has a leathery and earthy profile accompanied by notes of spice and pepper.
